OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,FA baby car seat is being urgently
OL,7,Frecalled because of an issue with its
OL,8,Fsafety indicator which poses a "risk
OL,9,Fof injuries" to children.
OL,11,FOwners of the Maxi-Cosi Family Fix
OL,12,FSlide Pro Base seat have been told to
OL,13,Fstop using the product immediately,
OL,14,Faccording to a recall alert from the
OL,15,FOffice for Product Safety and
OL,16,FStandards (OPSS).
OL,18,FThe baby car seat could detach from
OL,19,Fthe base as a result of the
OL,20,Fmalfunctioning indicator, the alert
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,F"The product presents a risk of
OL,7,Finjuries because the indicator, which
OL,8,Fshows whether the seat is correctly
OL,9,Ffitted, may display 'green' even when
OL,10,Fthe car seat is not fully attached to
OL,11,Fthe base," the OPSS warned.
OL,13,F"As a result, a user may believe the
OL,14,Fseat is properly connected when it is
OL,15,Fnot.
OL,17,F"This could cause the seat to move or
OL,18,Fdetach, potentially injuring the
OL,19,Foccupant."
OL,26,@sD@JO]uD@AOUyD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
