FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,FThe impacted products were made in
OL,7,FChina between September 6 2025 and
OL,8,FMarch 24 2026, Maxi-Cosi said.
OL,10,FUsers are urged to check their product
OL,11,Fby entering the product model
OL,12,Freference and manufacturing date on
OL,13,Fthe brand's website.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
