FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,FThe manufacturing date can be found on
OL,7,Fthe white label on the underside of
OL,8,Fthe car seat's base, and the reference
OL,9,Fnumber should contain 10 digits, the
OL,10,Fcompany said.
OL,12,F"Your child's safety drives every
OL,13,Fdecision we make at Maxi-Cosi, and in
OL,14,Fkeeping with our deep dedication to
OL,15,Fyou and your family, we want to make
OL,16,Fyou aware of a voluntary recall
OL,17,Faffecting your product," Maxi-Cosi
OL,18,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,F"During a recent user test conducted
OL,7,Fas part of our continuous improvement
OL,8,Fefforts to enhance ease of use, we
OL,9,Fidentified a potential misuse scenario
OL,10,Finvolving a visual indicator on our
OL,11,Fnew Maxi-Cosi FamilyFix base.
OL,13,F"We have initiated a voluntary product
OL,14,Frecall as part of our ongoing
OL,15,Fcommitment to the highest possible
OL,16,Fstandards of child safety, product
OL,17,Fquality, and ease of use."
OL,19,FSue Davies, Which? head of consumer
OL,20,Fprotection policy, said the recall was
OL,21,F"incredibly concerning".
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
