FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780067467
OL,3,CBaby car seat urgently recalled over
OL,4,C'risk of injuries'
OL,6,F"Max-Cosi and its suppliers must
OL,7,Furgently investigate how this has
OL,8,Fhappened and ensure the necessary
OL,9,Fsafeguards are in place to prevent
OL,10,Fpotentially unsafe products from
OL,11,Freaching consumers in future," Davies
OL,12,Fsaid.
